Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
init_mmmc_file(25.10)                                    init_mmmc_file(25.10)

Name
       init_mmmc_file

Syntax
         init_mmmc_file <file_name>

       Type: String

       Default: NULL

       Specifies a Tcl command script that contains the analysis view configu-
       rations  for  multi-mode  multi-corner (MMMC) timing analysis and opti-
       mization. If this view definition file is not in the current directory,
       specify the complete path to the file. The init_mmmc_file global  vari-
       able  replaces the previous rda_Input(ui_view_definition_file) configu-
       ration file variable.

Example
              * The following command specifies mmmc.tcl as the MMMC view def-
                inition file.

                set init_mmmc_file {mmmc.tcl}

Related Information
